-- Hollande’s Approval Rating Drops to 46%, Ifop Survey Reports
-- B y   H e l e n e   F o u q u e t
-- 2013-01-15T17:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-15/hollande-s-approval-rating-drops-to-46-ifop-survey-reports.html
French President  Francois Hollande ’s
approval rating fell one point to 46 percent in January, an Ifop
institute poll released today showed.  The survey for Paris Match magazine was conducted Jan. 10
and 11 among 1,018 people age 18 or older.  The Paris-based Ifop poll was taken before Hollande
announced France’s military intervention in Mali on Jan.11 and
has a margin of error of 2.8 percentage points  To contact the reporter on this story:
Helene Fouquet in Paris at 
 hfouquet1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
